# API Directory Structure

The `src/api` directory contains modules for interacting with backend APIs.

- [order.ts](mdc:src/api/order.ts): Functions for order-related API requests.
- [index.ts](mdc:src/api/index.ts): Main API entry point, may aggregate or export API functions.

## Usage
- Add new files here for additional API modules.
- Import and use API functions from this directory in your components or hooks.
